## 🎯 Phase 1: HandleFS 实现 (Week 1)

### 目标
实现有状态的文件句柄管理,支持大文件分块传输

### 核心设计

#### HandleFS 插件接口
```rust
pub trait HandleFS: EvifPlugin {
    /// 打开文件句柄
    async fn open_handle(
        &self,
        path: &str,
        flags: OpenFlags,
        mode: u32,
        lease: Duration,
    ) -> EvifResult<FileHandle>;

    /// 读取句柄
    async fn read_handle(
        &self,
        handle_id: i64,
        offset: i64,
        size: u64,
    ) -> EvifResult<Vec<u8>>;

    /// 写入句柄
    async fn write_handle(
        &self,
        handle_id: i64,
        data: Vec<u8>,
        offset: i64,
    ) -> EvifResult<u64>;

    /// 关闭句柄
    async fn close_handle(&self, handle_id: i64) -> EvifResult<()>;

    /// 刷新句柄
    async fn flush_handle(&self, handle_id: i64) -> EvifResult<()>;
}

/// 文件句柄
#[derive(Clone)]
pub struct FileHandle {
    pub id: i64,
    pub path: String,
    pub flags: OpenFlags,
    pub mode: u32,
    pub offset: i64,
    pub created_at: Instant,
    pub expires_at: Instant,
}

/// 打开标志
bitflags::bitflags! {
    pub struct OpenFlags: u32 {
        const READ_ONLY = 1 << 0;
        const WRITE_ONLY = 1 << 1;
        const READ_WRITE = 1 << 2;
        const CREATE = 1 << 3;
        const EXCLUSIVE = 1 << 4;
        const TRUNCATE = 1 << 5;
        const APPEND = 1 << 6;
        const NONBLOCK = 1 << 7;
    }
}
```

### REST API 端点
```
POST   /api/v1/handles                    - 打开文件句柄
GET    /api/v1/handles/:id                - 获取句柄信息
POST   /api/v1/handles/:id/read           - 从句柄读取
POST   /api/v1/handles/:id/write          - 向句柄写入
DELETE /api/v1/handles/:id                - 关闭句柄
POST   /api/v1/handles/:id/flush          - 刷新句柄
GET    /api/v1/handles                    - 列出所有句柄
```

