**附录: 测试命令**

```bash
# 测试所有已验证模块
cargo test --package evif-client \
             --package evif-graph \
             --package evif-protocol \
             --package evif-storage \
             --package evif-vfs \
             --package evif-grpc \
             --package evif-rest

# 测试单个模块
cargo test --package evif-client

# 查看测试详情
cargo test -- --nocapture

# 运行特定测试
cargo test test_client_config_default
```
